{"commentv2": 1, "number": 16, "id": 151755, "nreplies": 11, "sticky": 0, "user": "Vlad", "body": "I would like to warn you not to listen to this if you are progressing in Black Temple (or if you will be in closest future)! Otherwise if you are like me, someone who knows that Black Temple is totally out of your league, feel free to spoil hardcore! ;) Just notice that the sounds are not sorted in appearance order! That one is left for your imagination... :P\n\n[b]The prelude (quest chain?):[/b]\n\n[ul][li]/run PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Akama\\\\BTPRLUDE_Akama01.wav\");[/li]\n[li]/run PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Akama\\\\BTPRLUDE_Akama02.wav\");[/li]\n[li]/run PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Akama\\\\BTPRLUDE_Akama03.wav\");[/li]\n[li]/run PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Akama\\\\BTPRLUDE_Akama04.wav\");[/li]\n[li]/run PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Akama\\\\BTPRLUDE_Akama05.wav\");[/li]\n[li]/run PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Akama\\\\BTPRLUDE_Akama06.wav\");[/li]\n[li]/run PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Akama\\\\BTPRLUDE_Akama07.wav\");[/li]\n[li]/run PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Akama\\\\BTPRLUDE_Akama08.wav\");[/li]\n[li]/run PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Illidan\\\\BTPRLUDE_Illidan01.wav\");[/li]\n[li]/run PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Illidan\\\\BTPRLUDE_Illidan02.wav\");[/li]\n[li]/run PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Illidan\\\\BTPRLUDE_Illidan03.wav\");[/li][/ul]\n\n[b]Illidan in Black Temple:[/b]\n\n[ul][li]\"[b]Akama... your duplicity is hardly surprising. I should have slaughtered you and your malformed brethren long ago.[/b]\"\n/run PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Illidan\\\\BLACK_Illidan_01.wav\");[/li]\n\n[li]\"[b]Boldly said. But I remain unconvinced.[/b]\"\n/run PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Illidan\\\\BLACK_Illidan_02.wav\");[/li]\n\n[li]\"[b]Come my minnions, deal with this traitor as he deserves![/b]\"\n/run PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Illidan\\\\BLACK_Illidan_03.wav\");[/li]\n\n[li]\"[b]You are not prepared![/b]\"\n/run PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Illidan\\\\BLACK_Illidan_04.wav\");[/li]\n\n[li]\"[b]I can feel your hatred![/b]\"\n/run PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Illidan\\\\BLACK_Illidan_05.wav\");[/li]\n\n[li]\"[b]Give in to your fear![/b]\"\n/run PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Illidan\\\\BLACK_Illidan_06.wav\");[/li]\n\n[li]\"[b]You know nothing of power![/b]\"\n/run PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Illidan\\\\BLACK_Illidan_07.wav\");[/li]\n\n[li]\"[b]Feel the hatred of ten thousand years![/b]\"\n/run PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Illidan\\\\BLACK_Illidan_08.wav\");[/li]\n\n[li]\"[b]Such arrogance![/b]\"\n/run PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Illidan\\\\BLACK_Illidan_09.wav\");[/li]\n\n[li]\"[b]This is too easy![/b]\"\n/run PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Illidan\\\\BLACK_Illidan_10.wav\");[/li]\n\n[li]\"[b]Who shall be next to taste my blades?[/b]\"\n/run PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Illidan\\\\BLACK_Illidan_11.wav\");[/li]\n\n[li]\"[b]You've wasted too much time mortals. Now you shall fall![/b]\"\n/run PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Illidan\\\\BLACK_Illidan_12.wav\");[/li]\n\n[li]\"[b]Behold the power, of the demon within![/b]\"\n/run PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Illidan\\\\BLACK_Illidan_13.wav\");[/li]\n\n[li]\"[b]Is this it mortals, is this all the fury you can muster?[/b]\"\n/run PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Illidan\\\\BLACK_Illidan_14.wav\");[/li]\n\n[li]\"[b]Maiev, how is it even possible?[/b]\"\n/run PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Illidan\\\\BLACK_Illidan_15.wav\");[/li]\n\n[li]\"[b]You have won, Maiev. But the huntress is nothing without the hunt. You are nothing... without me![/b]\"\n/run PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Illidan\\\\BLACK_Illidan_16.wav\");[/li]\n\n[li]\"[b]I will not be touched by a rabbel such as you![/b]\"\n/run PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Illidan\\\\BLACK_Illidan_17.wav\");[/li]\n\n[li]\"[b]Behold the flames of Azzinoth![/b]\"\n/run PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Illidan\\\\BLACK_Illidan_18.wav\");[/li]\n\n[li]\"[b]Stare into the eyes of the betrayer![/b]\"\n/run PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Illidan\\\\BLACK_Illidan_19.wav\");[/li][/ul]\n\nIt's [i]7500 characters[/i] so I couldn't include Akama. Though if the interest gets that big I will... :P", "date": "2007-09-11T16:34:41-05:00", "rating": 242, "indent": 0, "roles": 256, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Open a model frame (i.e. character window) and paste the code while mousing over that frame. The mouse over frame will display the model of:  Akama: [b]/run GetMouseFocus():SetModel(\"CREATURE\\\\Akama\\\\Akama.mdx\");[/b]  Akamas weapon: [b]/run GetMouseFocus():SetModel(\"ITEM\\\\OBJECTCOMPONENTS\\\\WEAPON\\\\Sword_1H_Akama_D_01.mdx\");[/b]  Illidan: [b]/run GetMouseFocus():SetModel(\"CREATURE\\\\Illidan\\\\Illidan.mdx\");[/b]  Illidan (Dark Form): [b]/run GetMouseFocus():SetModel(\"CREATURE\\\\Illidan\\\\IllidanDark.mdx\");[/b]  Illidans Glaive (Warglaive of Azzinoth): [b]/run GetMouseFocus():SetModel(\"CREATURE\\\\Illi", "creationdate": "2007-09-11T16:34:42-05:00", "id": 313714, "rating": 102, "commentid": 151755, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "Vlad", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "You can view the sound files by using MyWarcraftStudio :)", "creationdate": "2007-09-29T05:50:08-05:00", "id": 312407, "rating": 11, "commentid": 151755, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "Vlad", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "[quote]while mousing over that frame.[/quote] Remember when you press enter for the code to work your mouse must be hovering over the model in your 'Character info' window ('c' By default)  (Reply to deleted comment)", "creationdate": "2009-01-15T11:45:27-06:00", "id": 72913, "rating": 35, "commentid": 151755, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "302803", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "[quote]\"Is this it mortals, is this all the fury you can master?\"[/quote]  \"...all the fury you can MUSTER?\"", "creationdate": "2009-09-27T22:54:46-05:00", "id": 124722, "rating": 31, "commentid": 151755, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "175354", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "lol Lord Marrowgar says : Is this it mortals, is this all the fury you can muster?, Who shall be next to taste my blades? ...", "creationdate": "2010-07-11T21:37:00-05:00", "id": 172633, "rating": 20, "commentid": 151755, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Fuyz", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2012-08-05T17:21:39-05:00", 9, "Vlad"]}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 17, "id": 155815, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Kanthalas", "body": "Actually your wrong.  Illidan -was- trained as a druid by Cenarius along side of Furion.  He eventually gave it up seeing his brother growing faster in it than him and went back to practicing arcane magic (Later its known that golden eyes indicate strong innate druidic magic in a Night Elf, and Illidan had golden eyes)\n\nAlso during the first War with the Burning Legion he was captured and struck a deal with Sargaras, Sargaras gave him magical powers and sight (The tattoos on his body and ripped out his eyes and replaced them with magic orbs basically) in return helping Sargaras come to this world.  So basically he helped Sargaras come partly in the world knowing his brother will destroy the Well of Eternity stopping him.  So he did betray both races sorta.  \n\nOh he also killed a demon called Azzinoth during that war which explains all the items.", "date": "2007-09-20T17:48:33-05:00", "rating": 125, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2007-09-20T18:18:48-05:00", 1, "Kanthalas"]}
