{"commentv2": 1, "number": 22, "id": 168201, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Vlad", "body": "Here are then the Akama sound files. Don't think there are any more missing from the Akama vs. Illidan event anymore. ;)\n\n[b]Akama in Black Temple:[/b]\n\n[ul][li]\"[b]Slay all who see us. Word must not kick back to Illidan![/b]\"\n/run PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Akama\\\\BLCKTMPLE_Akama_01.wav\");[/li]\n\n[li]\"[b]Now is the time Maiev, unleash your wrath![/b]\"\n/run PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Akama\\\\BLCKTMPLE_Akama_02.wav\");[/li]\n\n[li]\"[b]Akama has no master, not anymore.[/b]\"\n/run PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Akama\\\\BLCKTMPLE_Akama_03.wav\");[/li]\n\n[li]\"[b]Fight on friends, kill him and end the curse on my people![/b]\"\n/run PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Akama\\\\BLCKTMPLE_Akama_AkamaDies01.wav\");[/li]\n\n[li]\"[b]I'll deal with these mongrels. Strike now friends, strike at the betrayer![/b]\"\n/run PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Akama\\\\BLCKTMPLE_Akama_Defend01.wav\");[/li]\n\n[li]\"[b]We've come to end your reign Illidan, my people and all of outland shall be free![/b]\"\n/run PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Akama\\\\BLCKTMPLE_Akama_FightBgn01.wav\");[/li]\n\n[li]\"[b]The light will bless these dismal halls once again. I swear it![/b]\"\n/run PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Akama\\\\BLCKTMPLE_Akama_FinalWin01.wav\");[/li]\n\n[li]\"[b]The time has come, the moment is at hand.[/b]\"\n/run PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Akama\\\\BLCKTMPLE_Akama_Freed01.wav\");[/li]\n\n[li]\"[b]Uninvited guests.[/b]\"\n/run PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Akama\\\\BLCKTMPLE_Akama_Incmng01.wav\");[/li]\n\n[li]\"[b]There are more of them.[/b]\"\n/run PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Akama\\\\BLCKTMPLE_Akama_Incmng02.wav\");[/li]\n\n[li]\"[b]I will not last much longer.[/b]\"\n/run PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Akama\\\\BLCKTMPLE_Akama_LowHlth01.wav\");[/li]\n\n[li]\"[b]No, no yet![/b]\"\n/run PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Akama\\\\BLCKTMPLE_Akama_LowHlth02.wav\");[/li]\n\n[li]\"[b]Be weary friends, the betrayer meditates in the courts just beyond.[/b]\" [i](a bit unsure about what he said in the start of the sentence)[/i]\n/run PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Akama\\\\BLCKTMPLE_Akama_PreFight01.wav\");[/li]\n\n[li]\"[b]Illidan will pay![/b]\"\n/run PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Akama\\\\BLCKTMPLE_Akama_Slay01.wav\");[/li]\n\n[li]\"[b]One step closer![/b]\"\n/run PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Akama\\\\BLCKTMPLE_Akama_Slay02.wav\");[/li]\n\n[li]\"[b]Beware his gaze, do not look into his eyes![/b]\"\n/run PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Akama\\\\BLCKTMPLE_Akama_Warn01.wav\");[/li][/ul]\n\n[i]Have fun![/i] :)", "date": "2007-10-14T08:15:44-05:00", "rating": 147, "indent": 0, "roles": 256, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2007-10-14T08:24:08-05:00", 1, "Vlad"]}
