{"commentv2": 1, "number": 78, "id": 406802, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "225060", "body": "When Phase 1 Starts Let Akama Tank him , Akama got ~100,000 Health and Uses a BoK which Gives all Stats by 10% , Akama Can down illidan at 85% Then Illidan Will Call his minions to finish him Then you Make your Strike! ... Save your Shield Block / Enrage Abillity For Shear so you can Evade it ... When Phase 2 Comes Wait for Flames of Azzinoth to Summon .. When They Use Blaze .. Keep Them to Each other And They Will fight each other to death as a Glitch , Your Heals should Recover only The Fireball and Barrage , When he Turns into Demon Have a Priest / Warlock Tank him with Shadow Prot. / on Maiev's Phase Let Him Attack Her so She'd Tank him She's Not Healable but Uses ~800,000 Health and Shadowstrike Abillity Which Tanks him Nicely.", "date": "2008-10-15T11:55:34-05:00", "rating": -4, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "responseroles": "524", "responseuser": "thaia", "response": "Please use the formatting options only to highlight parts of your posts.", "lastEdit": ["2015-02-14T04:13:56-06:00", 1, "thaia"]}
