{"commentv2": 1, "number": 151, "id": 1153442, "nreplies": 3, "sticky": 0, "user": "LeminaAusa", "body": "According to the 2010 Blizzcon WoW quests and lore panel (mmo champion has it over here: http://www.mmo-champion.com/content/2035-Blizzcon-2010-WoW-Quests-and-Lore-Panel#new_comment), Metzen mentioned he was interested in resurrecting illidan as a character and giving him a redemption story. [quote]\r\n\r\nQ:Will we ever see a redemption or resurrection of Illidan as a Character?\r\nA: BOY DO I WANT TO DO THAT. That'd be badass. I don't think anyone at all has ever talked about that. But I love that #$%^. I'm a sucker for a good redemption story. Except Arthas. Not Arthas. He's dead.[/quote]\r\n\r\nSo it is possible he'll be back in the distant future. As long as he doesn't talk about setbacks, I'm fine with that.", "date": "2010-10-26T06:32:24-05:00", "rating": 25, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "He just said it like sarcrastic or playing, he wasn't talking srsly you should search the video of Q&A in Youtube.", "creationdate": "2010-10-29T14:57:58-05:00", "id": 461647, "rating": 3, "commentid": 1153442, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "540490", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "It depresses me greatly that Metzen seems so satisfied with how a rich anti-hero with [i]tons[/i] of story potential was written off and killed as a lackluster, throw-away villain.", "creationdate": "2010-10-29T23:08:22-05:00", "id": 461668, "rating": 7, "commentid": 1153442, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "457324", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Cue the \"O RLY\" from double-undead Menethil...", "creationdate": "2011-07-12T23:52:35-05:00", "id": 252019, "rating": 4, "commentid": 1153442, "dat