{"commentv2": 1, "number": 162, "id": 1495175, "nreplies": 2, "sticky": 0, "user": "393910", "body": "Some quests in Feralas have painted him in a more sympathetic light. And based on Tyrande's \"Leaders of Azeroth\" short story, his former comrades at least feel a little sorry for him. Glad the writers remembered that, whatever he may have become, at one point he at least -tried- to be a hero. \r\n\r\nDemon Hunters in general have been cast in a more positive light--there's Feronas Sindweller, who gave the aforementioned quest, as well as a Demon-Hunter centric quest in the Blasted Lands that shows--not only are Demon Hunters capable of sanity--they're also capable of camaraderie and sacrifice. \r\n\r\nThink Demon Hunters might be the next Hero Class?", "date": "2011-08-14T21:45:00-05:00", "rating": 22, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "If there wasn't a death knight past trauma, it could.", "creationdate": "2011-08-18T10:26:28-05:00", "id": 259259, "rating": 3, "commentid": 1495175, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Antkibo", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "So shall it be written, so shall it be done.", "creationdate": "2021-02-27T19:10:03-06:00", "id": 1454930, "rating": 0, "commentid": 1495175, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Hentaya", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
