{"commentv2": 1, "number": 166, "id": 1568682, "nreplies": 2, "sticky": 0, "user": "851681", "body": "Is it possible to kill him in 1 person as a rogue?", "date": "2011-11-10T10:35:32-06:00", "rating": -4, "indent": 0, "roles": 16384, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "I don't know if a Rogue can do it, but I wouldn't be surprised.", "creationdate": "2011-12-14T15:43:23-06:00", "id": 496963, "rating": 0, "commentid": 1568682, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "TheHeroOfTheDawn", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Nearly all BC bosses, including Illidan are easily soloed with proper preparation, excluding those fights that are impossible due to fight mechanics or DPS checks that your not going to meet. Spec for soloing raids by taking Imp Recup and Quickening, and if you don't want to lose a good enchant on your main weapons, pick up an extra set of daggers, pvp daggers will even work, and get the Mending enchant on them. Keep SnD up at all times and your good.", "creationdate": "2012-01-20T11:55:44-06:00", "id": 510075, "rating": 1, "commentid": 1568682, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "nkchri2", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
