{"commentv2": 1, "number": 168, "id": 1638408, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "TdarKoNe", "body": "Our two man team for taking down Illidan Stormrage in Black Temple every week:\nItem level 371 Blood Death Knight, 390 Elemental Shaman.\n\nI don't play my DK regularly, but he's the best character for the job with his ability to mitigate damage and self heal.\n\nStrategy: This fight is pretty simple with 2 level 85's in decent gear, phase one is tank and spank with standard \"get out of the fire\" technique.\n\nPhase 2: When he flies up into the air he will throw his warglaives into the ground, spawning two Flames of Azzinoth. The single MOST important thing to remember is to stay right in the middle of the warglaives. If you move the Flames too far away they will enrage and cause a whopping 500% more damage and it's extremely hard if not impossible to survive. Try to dodge the fire on the ground as much as you can but be sure not to stray too far away.\n\nPhase 3: Once the Flames are dead Illidan will come back down and it's basically phase 1 all over again.\n\nAfter this you pretty much just burn him down, I've never seen him get the chance to transform nor have we needed to use the trap on him. So beat him down and hopefully collect your warglaive!\n\nFull video on YouTube: www.youtube.com/watch?v=s4nLqBiXUR4&feature=share", "date": "2012-03-11T23:07:56-05:00", "rating": 7, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 1, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Best advice to farming this in a group is here: stay in the middle of the Flames of Azzinoth (http://www.wowhead.com/npc=22997/flame-of-azzinoth -- NOT \"warglaives\" which I believe is a slight inaccuracy in the OP's post but is confusing because there is a graphic of a glaive thrown down but only just to create the Flame of Azzinoth which will come from the glaive to your party). We had trouble on the 2nd phase until we just planted and DPS'ed the Flames down. I imagine this boss is pretty easy with a minimum compliment but we had a guild run (including Guild Achievement) with just 7 present.", "creationdate": "2012-06-10T11:16:36-05:00", "id": 548958, "rating": -1, "commentid": 1638408, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "Hairband", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2012-03-13T11:22:12-05:00", 1, "TdarKoNe"]}
