{"commentv2": 1, "number": 174, "id": 1701463, "nreplies": 3, "sticky": 0, "user": "Noxheart", "body": "Illidan is not a bad guy. Hes only trying to help. And if he now has become mad or insane its because of hes brother and tyrande. Its not illidans fault, he was trying to protect the ones he loved, but the betrayed him. Not the otherway around. No one can blame illidan for what hes done. I feel bad every time i kill him and i hope someday. We'll kill that traitor brother of his...", "date": "2012-08-18T17:45:29-05:00", "rating": 0, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Question. How much do you really know about Illidan? He never wanted to help. He wanted glory. He wanted to be the hero and get the girl. Never cared about anyone else.", "creationdate": "2012-09-04T20:16:36-05:00", "id": 568920, "rating": 1, "commentid": 1701463, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "Reignac", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "So he wanted the same as everyone else? Be imba, get full tier gear (solo - 3 expacs later), get the girl, a bit of glory then to go back to SW and flex?", "creationdate": "2013-01-25T08:09:38-06:00", "id": 626278, "rating": 1, "commentid": 1701463, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Firlox", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "There is a cool quest line about his story in felwood in the northern part after reaching the bigger druid village.", "creationdate": "2014-02-16T23:52:17-06:00", "id": 729529, "rating": 0, "commentid": 1701463, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "madmurdock", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "be