{"commentv2": 1, "number": 202, "id": 1887694, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "heartcrash", "body": "soloed on my 85 mw monk. mostly 415 mop blues, 442 mace, chest and cloak, 450 off hand and bracers, so easily obtainable gear from the ah and definitely not a twink.\r\n\r\ngot 10 stacks of mana tea and 4 chi before the pull just for extra. stay in the middle so the fire elementals do very little damage and besides that the fight is just very easy. soloed all of black temple with my 85 mw. definitely doable for most players without any difficulties.", "date": "2013-08-17T00:33:36-05:00", "rating": -4, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
