{"commentv2": 1, "number": 206, "id": 1917763, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Betonkocka", "body": "It was very easy with my ilvl 498 frost DK (no enchants, no gems, not even reforged to the right level, as this is just a slave alt)\r\nThe only one thing, which was mentioned that in P2 you have to stand in the middle and use some CD. Quickly dps down the 2 big adds. Funny thing that there are some puddles on the ground which are damaging you when you stand in them AND they have the same colour as the big adds. I just realized when one was already dead that I am still loosing HP; I was standing in this thingy. When I moved out, it was fine again, but then the other add was also dead.\r\n\r\nThe rest of the fight is easy.", "date": "2013-11-13T03:07:59-06:00", "rating": -5, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
