{"commentv2": 1, "number": 209, "id": 1928878, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "iluminati", "body": "As[u] Combat Rogue [/u]487 ilvl.\r\n\r\n[i][b]Save all your CDs for Phase 2.[/b][/i]\r\n\r\n[b]P1:[/b] [spell=73651] + Regular Rotation\r\n\r\n[b]P2:[/b] Go to the center of the scenario, use [spell=13877] and use all your CDs and Defensive CDs to kill the adds quickly.\r\n\r\n[u]Get away from green fire, it does a lot of damage.\r\nDont get away the adds from the center.[/u]\r\n\r\n\r\n[b]P3:[/b] [spell=73651] + Regular Rotation", "date": "2013-12-24T22:47:03-06:00", "rating": 9, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 1, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Thanks for this, i followed and worked great, lvl 535 combat Rogue. I did not need to use recuperate at all, But Stage 2 is the key, STAY IN THE MIDDLE and Blade furry as much as possible.", "creationdate": "2014-03-22T11:20:40-05:00", "id": 736138, "rating": 1, "commentid": 1928878, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "wgsx", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
