{"commentv2": 1, "number": 222, "id": 2226040, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "Manbewbs", "body": "He's back men and women.", "date": "2015-08-06T11:09:22-05:00", "rating": 1, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "I wonder if the model for his appearance in the Burning Crusade Expansion will be updated? They didn't do that for Garrosh, so seeing the old/uglier Garrosh everywhere until you finally landed in Draenor (and the old/lame Thrall until MoP content) was weird, especially since they DID update Vol'Jin's appearance everywhere.", "creationdate": "2015-08-06T14:11:51-05:00", "id": 890005, "rating": -1, "commentid": 2226040, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Luvas", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 223, "id": 2233509, "nreplies": 5, "sticky": 0, "user": "Saltura", "body": "I am surprised that no one has talked about this in official forums, on WowHead or any other places.\r\n\r\nJust like Naxxramas' removal with Wrath of the Lich King, I am guessing that Black Temple might be removed since Illidian is coming back. Do you think it would be the case for Black Temple? Would the items, especially the glaves, be unobtainable just like old Naxx items? I have most of the items and I have started to farm the glaves for a few other chars who can use them but I just wanted to know what others are thinking.", "date": "2015-08-17T00:57:19-05:00", "rating": -5, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "yeah but remember, Black temple is in outland and i really doubt that they will revamp outland, yes Illidan will return, but in Azeroth, i think they will not just remove the final boss of this old raid", "creationdate": "2015-08-19T17:56:31-05:00", "id": 893078, "rating": 1, "commentid": 2233509, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Lightharion", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "They just added an achievement that requires getting battle pets from the Black Temple, so I'd be surprised if they remove it.", "creationdate": "2015-10-03T17:44:46-05:00", "id": 902591, "rating": 1, "commentid": 2233509, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "voodoopimp", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "They wont remove him Illidan's defeat is part of the lore. That raid fits in the story. Illidan sent his demon hunters away when \"we\" started the siege of Black temple.", "creationdate": "2015-11-12T03:55:21-06:00", "id": 910517, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2233509, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "abris1995", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Blizzard doesn't make the game appear logical anymore. They did do that with Naxxramas yes, but I'm sure due to their newfound laziness, they'll just have Illidan run around in both places. Just like Dalaran and Acherus will be in two places at once.", "creationdate": "2016-01-01T17:38:25-06:00", "id": 922206, "rating": -1, "commentid": 2233509, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Sounalius", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Reason I think they will not remove it are: 1. They have already altered the Dark Portal to attune to Draenor so using the portal to Outland could be explained by the use of the Bronze Dragonflight as they do with certain areas and lands such as Theramore before it was destroyed. 2. Naxxramas was not removed, it was revamped and moved same as Onyxia's lair (not moved) and a few dungeons so Black Temple would be revamped if they wanted to. 3. As mentioned above it is part of recently released achievements, they may not have an intention to remove it.", "creationdate": "2016-02-19T13:13:45-06:00", "id": 930639, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2233509, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "ZeroGamer", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
