{"commentv2": 1, "number": 0, "id": 1584303, "nreplies": 5, "sticky": 0, "user": "DawnArchitect", "body": "Maybe it's my vision, or it's distorted user interface, but on his icon he looks very much like Agent Smith from \"The Matrix\".\r\n\r\nI think now we are TRULY prepared.", "date": "2011-11-30T06:27:44-06:00", "rating": 23, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "To think of it, the following quote is also characteristic for Illidan wiping raids:  \"Why, Mr. %PLAYER_NAME%? Why do you do it? Why get up? Why keep fighting? Do you believe you're fighting for something? For more than your survival? Can you tell me what it is? Do you even know? Is it freedom? Or truth? Perhaps peace? Could it be for love? Illusions, Mr. %PLAYER_NAME%. Vagaries of perception. The temporary constructs of a feeble human intellect trying desperately to justify an existence that is without meaning or purpose. And all of them as artificial as the Matrix itself. Although, only a hu", "creationdate": "2011-11-30T06:27:45-06:00", "id": 494762, "rating": 1, "commentid": 1584303, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "DawnArchitect", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "You hear that, Mr. Architect?... That is the sound of inevitability... It is the sound of your death... Goodbye, Mr. Architect...", "creationdate": "2011-11-30T13:44:43-06:00", "id": 281093, "rating": 1, "commentid": 1584303, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Agoonga", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Oh my gosh, my friends and I were saying the -exact same thing- when this instance came out. We'd queue, see the splash for WoE and go \"Yay! Hugo Weaving!\" Relatedly, I think it's a mixture of portrait angle and Illidan's expression. It's like a classic Agent Smith scowl.", "creationdate": "2012-04-02T09:48:07-05:00", "id": 532482, "rating": 1, "commentid": 1584303, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Seethe", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "I came here just to comment that, but seems like someone else did lol", "creationdate": "2012-06-03T15:03:40-05:00", "id": 547568, "rating": 0, "commentid": 1584303, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "587126", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Notice the similarities between his charactier icon and Hugo Weaving, the actor who portrayed Agent Smith and Elrond in LOTR. It would have been sooooooooooooooo EPIC if Blizz would have used him to voice Illidan.", "creationdate": "2012-07-16T17:57:43-05:00", "id": 557301, "rating": 2, "commentid": 1584303, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Oberheim", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
