{"commentv2": 1, "number": 3, "id": 675726, "nreplies": 2, "sticky": 0, "user": "206795", "body": "lol Illadin was a DEMON HUNTER now he`s a DEMON thats wierd!", "date": "2009-04-14T01:36:44-05:00", "rating": -3, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Demon Hunters eventually become that of a Demon. That's their goal - to containt the powers of the Demon they trap inside themselves and continue to sap power from the Demon based on nothing but absolute will power.  The Demon Hunter feeds off its Fel Energy and uses it as a weapon against the Legion. Basically fighting fire with fire.  And although Demon Hunters are not widely accepted in civilization, many do respect and fear Demon Hunters for their efforts to bring about the Legion's end.  Here's more on Demon Hunters. http://www.wowwiki.com/Demon_hunter", "creationdate": "2009-04-27T13:21:59-05:00", "id": 94377, "rating": 12, "commentid": 675726, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "341694", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Vennarok: so a little like Kirby.", "creationdate": "2014-07-31T04:52:44-05:00", "id": 761356, "rating": 1, "commentid": 675726, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "cephadex", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 4, "id": 690889, "nreplies": 4, "sticky": 0, "user": "Ag3nt007", "body": "if there is some true power on the lich king i say it  comes more from the soul of Ner'Zhul", "date": "2009-04-23T14:43:35-05:00", "rating": 4, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Actually, its Arthas's and Ner'zul's soul trapped inside Arthas's body, so if anything its probarily Arthas which would be the more powerful of the two.", "creationdate": "2009-06-17T11:51:21-05:00", "id": 104294, "rating": 1, "commentid": 690889, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "craftyard", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "in Rise of the Lich king, it is revealed that ner'zul's soul was killed by arthas therefore the lich king is now arthas and only arthas", "creationdate": "2009-08-01T09:53:32-05:00", "id": 113100, "rating": 0, "commentid": 690889, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "266135", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "[quote]in Rise of the Lich king, it is revealed that ner'zul's soul was killed by arthas therefore the lich king is now arthas and only arthas[/quote]  Wrong. Arthas has killed his spirit aswell (the child, wich is obiviously a reference to Mathias Lerner, or whatever he is spelt). There's just the Lich King now. No Arthas, no Ner'zhul. As in a quest, LK states \"shamanism? Hah... i was a shaman, once...\" That means that, while Arthas rules above Ner'zhul, the spirit of both is now trapped inside the Lich King.", "creationdate": "2010-10-04T13:12:39-05:00", "id": 185004, "rating": 2, "commentid": 690889, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "MalygosHelper", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "MalygosHelper: neither of their spirits was really \"killed\" - as you state at the end of your comment, I think it's more correct to say both their spirits are trapped inside. Hence it makes sense that he had kept Jaina's locket all that time (I think on finding it she says something like \"I knew he was trapped in there\").", "creationdate": "2014-07-31T04:49:18-05:00", "id": 761353, "rating": 0, "commentid": 690889, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "cephadex", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
