{"commentv2": 1, "number": 0, "id": 1587048, "nreplies": 3, "sticky": 0, "user": "taigus", "body": "If you have the Warglaives of Azzinoth with you, Illidan will make a comment after you kill Peroth'arn:\r\n\r\nIllidan Stormrage says: Curious weapons you wield... such power.\r\nIllidan Stormrage says: You seem prepared.\r\n\r\nUnfortunately only the wielder will see this message, so others in the group won't get to enjoy it.", "date": "2011-12-02T02:30:45-06:00", "rating": 61, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Does it have to be the set (both weapons) or does he also say this if you only have one?", "creationdate": "2011-12-05T11:40:28-06:00", "id": 283676, "rating": 0, "commentid": 1587048, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "578455", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "You don't actually have to be wielding the Warglaives, he'll say it if you simply have them in your inventory. I'm guessing it either looks at your inventory, or it looks at your achievements, and if you have the achievement for the glaives, it will trigger the text.", "creationdate": "2011-12-07T02:47:15-06:00", "id": 284551, "rating": 2, "commentid": 1587048, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Ketala", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "A very pleasant easter egg. :D", "creationdate": "2012-01-08T00:47:27-06:00", "id": 506060, "rating": 2, "commentid": 1587048, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Aliok", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
