{"commentv2": 1, "number": 4, "id": 1588389, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "Senka", "body": "This will be really long and I doubt anyone actually cares to read almost the entire dungeon, but because I wasn't sure exactly what sections you wanted I just ended up typing all of Illidan's scenes. I think I missed the first and last dialogue boxes unfortunately.\r\nThe style might be a little confusing, sorry.  Anything in quotes and unnamed is Illidan talking.\r\n\r\n*After slaying the first Legion Demon*\r\n[quote]\"Over here, in the shadows.\"\r\n\"I think we stand a better chance fighting alongside one another.\"\r\n\r\nDialogue Box:\r\nThe shadows will hide us well.\r\n\r\nI am concealed by this shadowcloak, and can imbue its magics onto you.\r\n\r\nIt will not make us invisible, but as long as we keep our distance from our foes we will remain hidden.\r\n*Talk option: I am ready to be hidden by your shadowcloak.*\r\n\r\n*Illidan casts [url=http://www.wowhead.com/spell=105915]Shadowcloak[/url]*\r\n\"We now hide in shadows, hidden from our enemies.\"\r\n\r\nDialogue Box:\r\nAnything outside of that circle around you will not be able to see you, but the illusion will fade if you attack or take damage.\r\n\r\nI suggest you remain hidden until I say otherwise, these demons are too powerful to face head on and in full force.\r\n*Talk option: Let's go!*\r\n\r\n\"Come with me if you'd like to live long enough to see me save this world!\"[/quote]\r\n\r\nGeneric Lines:\r\n[quote]Illidan waits at an enemy group: \"I'll let you have the first kill. Don't make me regret that.\" \"They stand unaware that their deaths are moments away.\"\r\nIllidan attacks: \"Death to the Legion!\" \"My blades hunger.\"\r\nGroup at the focus is slain: \"Destroy the portal energy focus!\" \"Destroy the crystal so we can move on.\"\r\nUpon focus being destroyed: \"We're leaving. Stay close.\"[/quote]\r\n\r\n[quote]*Illidan proceeds to Courtyard of Lights*\r\n\"I've seen a single Guardian Demon slaughter a hundred elves. Tread lightly.\"\r\n\"I will hold them back so we can get past. Be ready.\"\r\n*Illidan casts [url=http://www.wowhead.com/spell=104400]Wall of Shadow[/url]; some time after...*\r\n\"My magic is fading. I'm going through!\"\r\n*Guardian Demon is alerted to the first portal*\r\n\"They will get what they deserve, in due time.\"\r\n*Illidan moves past the second portal*\r\n\"The stench of sulfur and brimstone... These portals are as foul as the demons themselves.\"\r\n*Approaching last focus*\r\n\"Let us shut down this final portal and finish this.\"\r\n*Illidan moves to the edge of the courtyard after the final focus is destroyed*\r\n\"The demons should all be leaving. We will be at the palace in no time.\"\r\n*Peroth'arn appears at the top of the stairs*\r\nPeroth'arn: \"Who shut down the portals? Clever little worms.\"\r\n\"The demons are no longer pouring from the palace. We can move ahead.\"\r\n*Illidan moves to the center of the courtyard*\r\n\"Too easy.\"[/quote]\r\n\r\n*Moments before Peroth'arn appears*\r\n[quote]\"Another demon, ready to be slaughtered.\"\r\nPeroth'arn: \"None will reach the palace without besting Peroth'arn, first of fel-touched!\"  \"No mortal may stand before me and live!\"\r\n\"Nothing will stop me. Not even you, demon.\"\r\n*Peroth'arn casts [url=http://www.wowhead.com/spell=104905]Drain Essence[/url]*\r\nPeroth'arn: \"Your essence... is MINE.\"\r\n\"Your magic is pathetic. Let me show you mine.\"\r\n*Illidan casts [url=http://www.wowhead.com/spell=105543]Absorb Fel Energy[/url]*\r\nPeroth'arn: \"The shadows serve ME, now...\"\r\n*Peroth'arn vanishes into the shadows!*\r\n\"[url=http://www.wowhead.com/spell=105635]Return to the shadows[/url]!\"\r\n*After some time of evading the Eyes of Peroth'arn...*\r\n\"My strength returns.\"\r\n*Peroth'arn is slain*\r\n\"The hunter became the prey.\"[/quote]\r\n\r\nDialogue Box:\r\n[quote]Such a foolish creature, trying to challenge us.  His rancid corpse will serve as a reminder to the Legion of the power of Illidan Stormrage.\r\n\r\nThe shadowcloak's magic is fading, concealing us no longer.  It was fun while it lasted, but I prefer a more direct approach to bringing death to my enemy.\r\n\r\nYou fought well, but where I'm heading I need to go alone.\r\n*Single talk option: Farewell, and good luck.*\r\n\"You did well, but for now I must continue alone. Good hunting.\"[/quote]\r\n\r\n*Later, in front of the Well area*\r\n[quote]\"Can you close the portal, brother?\"\r\nMalfurion Stormrage: \"It is being maintained by the will of a powerful demon...Mannoroth.\"  \"I cannot break his will alone...\"\r\n\"Very well, we shall break it for you.\"\r\nTyrande Whisperwind: \"He knows what we attempt. We have not much time, the forest crawls with his demons.\"\r\n\"Let them come.\"\r\nTyrande Whisperwing: \"Mother moon, guide us through this darkness.\"\r\n*Tyrande gains the [url=http://www.wowhead.com/spell=103917]Blessing of Elune[/url] and slays the waves of doomguards*\r\n\"Weak, pitiful creatures. Hardly worth of being called a legion.\r\n*Illidan walks up and meets an Abyssal Doombringer*\r\n\"Oh this will be fun...\"\r\n\"Wait, I have an idea.\"\r\nTyrande Whisperwind: \"Illidan, what is in that vial? What are you doing?\"\r\n\"What our people could not.\"\r\n*Illidan douses himself with the [url=http://www.wowhead.com/spell=103952]Waters of Eternity[/url]!*\r\n\"Yes...YES. I can feel the raw power of the Well of Eternity! It is time to end this charade!\"\r\n*When fighting the Highguard Elites and their Shadowbat mounts cast [url=http://www.wowhead.com/spell=103763]Displacement[/url]*\r\nTyrande whisperwind: \"I cannot strike them! What is this demon magic?\"\r\n\"They are not where they appear to be! Strike in an area, it is the only way to uncover the real one!\"\r\n*The Elites are slain*\r\n\"Handle Varo'then. Mannoroth is mine.\"[/quote]\r\n\r\n*After throwing Varo'then's sword at Mannoroth*\r\n[quote]\"The sword has pierced his infernal armor! Strike him down!\"\r\n*Mannoroth opens a Nether Portal to call Felguards*\r\n\"He is still connected to the Well somehow! Focus your attacks on Mannoroth, we must disrupt his concentration!\"\r\n*Infernals rain from the sky!*\r\nTyrande Whisperwind: \"There are too many of them!\"\r\n*Tyrande collapses! The Light of Elune winks out!*\r\n\"You are not the sole wielder of Sargeras's power, Mannoroth! Behold!\"\r\n*Illidan begins casting [url=http://www.wowhead.com/spell=104998]Gift of Sargeras[/url]*\r\nTyrande Whisperwind: \"Illidan...you mustn't!\"\r\n\"I will be the savior of our people! I WILL FULFILL MY DESTINY!\"\r\nTyrande Whisperwind: \"No! Illidan!\"\r\n\"[Demonic] Revos ill ok mordanas archim maz naztheros! Archim xi ante maz-re mishun te nagas!\"[/quote]\r\n\r\n*Mannoroth is pulled into the well with the Dragon Soul and Illidan leaps to the well's edge*\r\n[quote]\"The artifact!\"\r\n\"Brother. A timely arrival...\"\r\nMalfurion Stormrage: \"Illidan! The well is out of control!\"\r\n\"Aye. It's been twisted and turned by too many spells. The fuss we - especially you - made with the portal was too much! The same spell that sent the Burning Legion back into their foul realm now works on the well! It's devouring itself and taking its surroundings with it! Fascinating, isn't it?\"\r\nMalfurion Stormrage: \"Not if we're caught up in it! Why weren't you running? What have you been doing with your hand in the Well?\"\r\n\"If you've a way out of here, we should probably use it! I've tried casting myself and Tyrande out of here, but the well is too much in flux!\"\r\nMalfurion Stormrage: \"This way!\"[/quote]", "date": "2011-12-03T19:12:54-06:00", "rating": 21, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "I was actually interested in the dialoge boxes since those are read only and disapears as soon as someone clicks the conversaton option. The others are easily readable in the chatframe but thanks for the effort =)", "creationdate": "2011-12-06T09:41:52-06:00", "id": 284216, "rating": 0, "commentid": 1588389, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Alexj", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2011-12-14T01:36:55-06:00", 10, "Senka"]}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 5, "id": 1596110, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Paulizzfun", "body": "He was a practitioner of Highborne magic. In his youth, he attempted to master the druidic forces as his brother had, but the sorcery called to him in a way that the magic of the land did not. Unlike his brother, Illidan was born with amber eyes; at the time, this was regarded by the elves as a sign of a great destiny\u2014 however, this actually indicated inherent druidic potential.", "date": "2011-12-14T14:44:07-06:00", "rating": 4, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
