{"commentv2": 1, "number": 0, "id": 1181610, "nreplies": 3, "sticky": 0, "user": "Leishai", "body": "[url=http://www.wowhead.com/npc=47923]Feronas Sindweller[/url] in Felwood gives you a quest. A memory of [url=http://www.wowhead.com/npc=47733]Arthas[/url] and [url=http://www.wowhead.com/npc=47819]Illidan[/url] appears after you accepted it. You have to help Illidan fighting during this memory. For the 1st quest you help Illidan fighting against Arthas. After the fight Arthas tells Illidan about the Skull of Gul'dan corrupting Felwood. For the 2nd quest you help Illidan getting the Skull of Gul'dan. For the 3rd quest you help Illidan fighting against [url=http://www.wowhead.com/npc=47917]Tichondrius[/url]. After this you get a 4th quest where [url=http://www.wowhead.com/npc=48135]Tyrande Whisperwind[/url] and [url=http://www.wowhead.com/npc=48134]Malfurion Stormrage[/url] talk to Illidan.\r\n[quote]Malfurium Stormrage says: Foul demon! What have you done with my brother?\r\nIllidan Stormrage says: It is I, Malfurion. This is what I've become.\r\nTyrande Whisperwind says: No! Illidan, how could you?\r\nIllidan Stormrage says: The leader of the undead has been destroyed, and the forests will heal in time.\r\nMalfurium Stormrage says: At the cost of your soul? You are no brother of mine! Begone from this place, and never set foot in our lands again![/quote]", "date": "2010-11-24T13:11:05-06:00", "rating": 8, "indent": 0, "roles": 256, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "You would think Malfurion would be more greatful.", "creationdate": "2011-02-19T16:49:29-06:00", "id": 226517, "rating": 10, "commentid": 1181610, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Palafied", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Since Malfurion didn't knew what Illidan knew he has a completely different view on the actions of his brother. This coin like all has two sides.", "creationdate": "2011-08-27T10:29:44-05:00", "id": 260967, "rating": 2, "commentid": 1181610, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "Leishai", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "The quest he gives is called \"A Destiny of Flame and Sorrow.\" It can be obtained from him after you do a number of prerequisites, namely: Running Their Course, Squirrely Clean, Weeding the Lawn, Nature and Nurture, Buzzers for Baby, Seeking Soil, These Roots were made for Stompin', Singin' in the Sun, The Last Protector, and Rejoining the Forest. Once those are done, the quest Wanted: The Demon Hunter will open to you, and you'll be directed to Feronas, who will give you the Illidan quests after you try slaying him.", "creationdate": "2014-08-01T02:28:53-05:00", "id": 761569, "rating": 1, "commentid": 1181610, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "cephadex", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
