{"commentv2": 1, "number": 0, "id": 1181567, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Leishai", "body": "[url=http://www.wowhead.com/npc=47923]Feronas Sindweller[/url] in Felwood gives you a quest. A memory of [url=http://www.wowhead.com/npc=47733]Arthas[/url] and [url=http://www.wowhead.com/npc=47819]Illidan[/url] appears after you accepted it. You have to help Illidan fighting during this memory. For the 1st quest you help Illidan fighting against Arthas. After the fight Arthas tells Illidan about the Skull of Gul'dan corrupting Felwood. For the 2nd quest you help Illidan getting the Skull of Gul'dan. For the 3rd quest you help Illidan fighting against [url=http://www.wowhead.com/npc=47917]Tichondrius[/url]. After this you get a 4th quest where [url=http://www.wowhead.com/npc=48135]Tyrande Whisperwind[/url] and [url=http://www.wowhead.com/npc=48134]Malfurion Stormrage[/url] talk to Illidan.\n[quote]Malfurium Stormrage says: Foul demon! What have you done with my brother?\nIllidan Stormrage says: It is I, Malfurion. This is what I've become.\nTyrande Whisperwind says: No! Illidan, how could you?\nIllidan Stormrage says: The leader of the undead has been destroyed, and the forests will heal in time.\nMalfurium Stormrage says: At the cost of your soul? You are no brother of mine! Begone from this place, and never set foot in our lands again![/quote]", "date": "2010-11-24T12:59:42-06:00", "rating": 12, "indent": 0, "roles": 256, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2011-08-27T10:27:48-05:00", 1, "Leishai"]}
