{"commentv2": 1, "number": 2, "id": 768207, "nreplies": 4, "sticky": 0, "user": "shurikhan2", "body": "what is an outland demon overlord (that was supposed to be ultimately destroyed) doing in icecrown?", "date": "2009-07-05T03:44:54-05:00", "rating": 0, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Kil'Jaeden had instructed Illidan to destroy The Lich King, after providing him with dark powers. Having failed, he moved to The Outlands to hide from KJ while rulling that world, from The Black Temple. However, he was found by Kil'Jaeden, who made an ultimatum: either he destroyed The Lich King, as intended, or he would feel the wrath of KJ. That lead Illidan to Icecrown.  By that time, The Lich King felt danger and summoned Arthas to him. The two (Arthas and Illidan) met in Icecrown, where they fought, Arthas being victorious (as is shown in this quest). So in Black Temple we face the story ", "creationdate": "2009-07-05T03:44:55-05:00", "id": 415694, "rating": 3, "commentid": 768207, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "425812", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Illidan did infact die at the end of the black temple, the quote regarding maiev was merely eluding to the fact that no that illidan is dead, she has no more of a purpose in life. I can assure you that illidan is dead. I looted his dead corpse.  http://www.wowwiki.com/Illidan_Stormrage#Death", "creationdate": "2009-08-11T20:17:27-05:00", "id": 115479, "rating": -1, "commentid": 768207, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "223788", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Kael'Thas...", "creationdate": "2009-08-31T09:25:30-05:00", "id": 422910, "rating": 0, "commentid": 768207, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "gamerunknown", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Actually Illidan died. He says \"Maiev... you have won... but the hunter... is nothing without the hunt... you are nothing without...me...\" That implies he died.", "creationdate": "2010-10-04T14:44:58-05:00", "id": 185015, "rating": -1, "commentid": 768207, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "MalygosHelper", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}